cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper deals with fine-grained classification and recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning networks (cs.LG) and the use of supervised learning (cs.AI) for training the network. Additionally, the paper deals with the use of convolutional neural networks (cs.MM) and keypoint localization (cs.NE) for fine-grained recognition.
